ActGwich'in Land Claim Settlement Act
PrecisOrder approving an amendment to be made to the GWICH'IN COMPREHENSIVE LAND CLAIM AGREEMENT which allows a settlement corporation of the Tribal Council to make more than one distribution of capital to each Gwich'in participant, to a maximum cumulative amount.
